OL,3,CSydney shark attack victim says first
OL,4,Cwords after briefly waking up from coma
OL,6,FA 34-year-old woman who was attacked
OL,7,Fby a shark more than a week ago at a
OL,8,Fpopular beach in Sydney has briefly
OL,9,Fwoken up from an induced coma, her
OL,10,Ffamily has said in an update.
OL,12,FLeah Stewart sustained life-
OL,13,Fthreatening injuries after she was
OL,14,Fattacked while swimming close to the
OL,15,Fshore on Coogee Beach on June 13.
OL,17,FShe has been on life support and had
OL,18,Fmultiple surgeries since the attack,
OL,19,Fincluding having her arm amputated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
