OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782326889
OL,3,CSydney shark attack victim says first
OL,4,Cwords after briefly waking up from coma
OL,6,FIn an update, her brother, Joshua, has
OL,7,Fshared Leah's first words after
OL,8,Fdoctors reduced her level of sedation
OL,9,Fto allow her to briefly wake up.
OL,11,FLeah's first words were "I love you",
OL,12,Fwhich she said to her mum and partner,
OL,13,Fwho have "been by her side in ICU
OL,14,Fsince the incident", Joshua said.
OL,16,FPosting on their GoFundMe page, he
OL,17,Fadded: "Her first thoughts were with
OL,18,Fher daughter August and wanted to
OL,19,Fcheck she was OK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782326889
OL,3,CSydney shark attack victim says first
OL,4,Cwords after briefly waking up from coma
OL,6,F"This is a lot faster than anyone
OL,7,Fexpected, and for us this feels like a
OL,8,Fmiracle and is everything so many of
OL,9,Fus have hoped and prayed for over the
OL,10,Fpast week."
OL,12,FHe said Leah remains in the intensive
OL,13,Fcare unit and has undergone five days
OL,14,Fof surgery since the attack, with more
OL,15,Fsurgeries to come.
OL,17,FHe continued: "Leah has a long road
OL,18,Fahead and still remains in critical
OL,19,Fcare, but this is such a positive
OL,20,Ffirst step and gives us hope for
OL,21,FLeah's long-term recovery."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
