OL,3,CSydney shark attack victim says first
OL,4,Cwords after briefly waking up from coma
OL,6,FShark attacks in Australia have become
OL,7,Fmore common over recent decades as the
OL,8,Fpopulation has grown and activities
OL,9,Fsuch as surfing and scuba diving have
OL,10,Fgained popularity.
OL,12,FThere have already been several shark
OL,13,Fattack fatalities in Australia this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FThree spearfishing divers have been
OL,17,Fkilled by sharks off the Australian
OL,18,Fcoast since May 16, bringing the total
OL,19,Fof fatalities in the nation this year
OL,20,Fto four.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
