CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782326889
OL,3,CSydney shark attack victim says first
OL,4,Cwords after briefly waking up from coma
OL,6,FIn January, a 12-year-old boy died in
OL,7,Fa hospital days after he was mauled by
OL,8,Fa bull shark in Sydney Harbor.
OL,10,FAustralia has averaged between two and
OL,11,Fthree fatal shark attacks a year since
OL,12,F2000, according to the Australian
OL,13,FShark Incident Database, a partnership
OL,14,Fof the Taronga Conservation Society
OL,15,FAustralia, Flinders University and the
OL,16,FNew South Wales state government.
OL,18,FLast year, Australia recorded five
OL,19,Ffatal shark attacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
